channel.title: What the crap
channel.description: So I logged into runescape today. I logged in 6 days ago, but the armour update wasn't there. 6 days later, I see the armour update, and i'm all. 'What the balls?" All confused, thinking it's a different item. Little was I wrong. It's updated. And looks like shit. I love the old RS better... Wish they'd bring that shit back.
